{
  "video_id": "BwOd20Mv0hM",
  "title": "Anil Ananthaswamy: What it takes to do extreme astrophysics",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15330.0,
      "end_time": 17330.0,
      "text": "I would like to talk today"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17330.0,
      "end_time": 19330.0,
      "text": "about what I think is one of the greatest adventures"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19330.0,
      "end_time": 21330.0,
      "text": "human beings have embarked upon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21330.0,
      "end_time": 24330.0,
      "text": "which is the quest to understand the universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24330.0,
      "end_time": 26330.0,
      "text": "and our place in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26330.0,
      "end_time": 29330.0,
      "text": "My own interest in this subject, and my passion for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29330.0,
      "end_time": 31330.0,
      "text": "began rather accidentally."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31330.0,
      "end_time": 34330.0,
      "text": "I had bought a copy of this book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34330.0,
      "end_time": 36330.0,
      "text": "\"The Universe and Dr. Einstein\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36330.0,
      "end_time": 39330.0,
      "text": "a used paperback from a secondhand bookstore in Seattle."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39330.0,
      "end_time": 42330.0,
      "text": "A few years after that, in Bangalore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42330.0,
      "end_time": 44330.0,
      "text": "I was finding it hard to fall asleep one night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44330.0,
      "end_time": 46330.0,
      "text": "and I picked up this book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46330.0,
      "end_time": 48330.0,
      "text": "thinking it would put me to sleep in 10 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48330.0,
      "end_time": 50330.0,
      "text": "And as it happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50330.0,
      "end_time": 53330.0,
      "text": "I read it from midnight to five in the morning in one shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53330.0,
      "end_time": 56330.0,
      "text": "And I was left with this intense feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56330.0,
      "end_time": 58330.0,
      "text": "of awe and exhilaration"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58330.0,
      "end_time": 60330.0,
      "text": "at the universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60330.0,
      "end_time": 63330.0,
      "text": "and our own ability to understand as much as we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63330.0,
      "end_time": 66330.0,
      "text": "And that feeling hasn&#39;t left me yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66330.0,
      "end_time": 68330.0,
      "text": "That feeling was the trigger for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68330.0,
      "end_time": 70330.0,
      "text": "to actually change my career --"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70330.0,
      "end_time": 73330.0,
      "text": "from being a software engineer to become a science writer --"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73330.0,
      "end_time": 76330.0,
      "text": "so that I could partake in the joy of science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76330.0,
      "end_time": 79330.0,
      "text": "and also the joy of communicating it to others."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79330.0,
      "end_time": 81330.0,
      "text": "And that feeling also led me"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81330.0,
      "end_time": 83330.0,
      "text": "to a pilgrimage of sorts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83330.0,
      "end_time": 85330.0,
      "text": "to go literally to the ends of the earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85330.0,
      "end_time": 88330.0,
      "text": "to see telescopes, detectors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88330.0,
      "end_time": 91330.0,
      "text": "instruments that people are building, or have built,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91330.0,
      "end_time": 93330.0,
      "text": "in order to probe the cosmos"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 93330.0,
      "end_time": 95330.0,
      "text": "in greater and greater detail."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95330.0,
      "end_time": 97330.0,
      "text": "So it took me from places like Chile --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97330.0,
      "end_time": 99330.0,
      "text": "the Atacama Desert in Chile --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 99330.0,
      "end_time": 101330.0,
      "text": "to Siberia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101330.0,
      "end_time": 103330.0,
      "text": "to underground mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103330.0,
      "end_time": 105330.0,
      "text": "in the Japanese Alps, in Northern America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 105330.0,
      "end_time": 107330.0,
      "text": "all the way to Antarctica"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 107330.0,
      "end_time": 109330.0,
      "text": "and even to the South Pole."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 109330.0,
      "end_time": 111330.0,
      "text": "And today I would like to share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 111330.0,
      "end_time": 114330.0,
      "text": "some images, some stories of these trips."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 114330.0,
      "end_time": 116330.0,
      "text": "I have been basically spending the last few years"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116330.0,
      "end_time": 118330.0,
      "text": "documenting the efforts"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 118330.0,
      "end_time": 121330.0,
      "text": "of some extremely intrepid men and women"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121330.0,
      "end_time": 123330.0,
      "text": "who are putting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123330.0,
      "end_time": 125330.0,
      "text": "literally at times, their lives at stake"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 125330.0,
      "end_time": 128329.0,
      "text": "working in some very remote and very hostile places"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 128330.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132330.0,
      "text": "so that they may gather the faintest signals from the cosmos"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 132330.0,
      "end_time": 135330.0,
      "text": "in order for us to understand this universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 135330.0,
      "end_time": 137330.0,
      "text": "And I first begin with a pie chart --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 137330.0,
      "end_time": 139330.0,
      "text": "and I promise this is the only pie chart"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 139330.0,
      "end_time": 141330.0,
      "text": "in the whole presentation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 141330.0,
      "end_time": 145330.0,
      "text": "but it sets up the state of our knowledge of the cosmos."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145330.0,
      "end_time": 148330.0,
      "text": "All the theories in physics that we have today"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 148330.0,
      "end_time": 150330.0,
      "text": "properly explain what is called normal matter --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150330.0,
      "end_time": 152330.0,
      "text": "the stuff that we&#39;re all made of --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 152330.0,
      "end_time": 154330.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s four percent of the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 154330.0,
      "end_time": 157330.0,
      "text": "Astronomers and cosmologists and physicists think"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 157330.0,
      "end_time": 160330.0,
      "text": "that there is something called dark matter in the universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 160330.0,
      "end_time": 162330.0,
      "text": "which makes up 23 percent of the universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 162330.0,
      "end_time": 164330.0,
      "text": "and something called dark energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 164330.0,
      "end_time": 166330.0,
      "text": "which permeates the fabric of space-time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 166330.0,
      "end_time": 168330.0,
      "text": "that makes up another 73 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168330.0,
      "end_time": 171330.0,
      "text": "So if you look at this pie chart, 96 percent of the universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171330.0,
      "end_time": 173330.0,
      "text": "at this point in our exploration of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 173330.0,
      "end_time": 176330.0,
      "text": "is unknown or not well understood."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 176330.0,
      "end_time": 179330.0,
      "text": "And most of the experiments, telescopes that I went to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179330.0,
      "end_time": 182330.0,
      "text": "are in some way addressing this question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 182330.0,
      "end_time": 185330.0,
      "text": "these two twin mysteries of dark matter and dark energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 185330.0,
      "end_time": 187330.0,
      "text": "I will take you first to an underground mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187330.0,
      "end_time": 189330.0,
      "text": "in Northern Minnesota"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 189330.0,
      "end_time": 191330.0,
      "text": "where people are looking"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 191330.0,
      "end_time": 193330.0,
      "text": "for something called dark matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 193330.0,
      "end_time": 196330.0,
      "text": "And the idea here is that they are looking for a sign"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196330.0,
      "end_time": 199330.0,
      "text": "of a dark matter particle hitting one of their detectors."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 199330.0,
      "end_time": 201330.0,
      "text": "And the reason why they have to go underground"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 201330.0,
      "end_time": 204330.0,
      "text": "is that, if you did this experiment on the surface of the Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 204330.0,
      "end_time": 206330.0,
      "text": "the same experiment would be swamped by signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 206330.0,
      "end_time": 208330.0,
      "text": "that could be created by things like cosmic rays,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 208330.0,
      "end_time": 210330.0,
      "text": "ambient radio activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 210330.0,
      "end_time": 213330.0,
      "text": "even our own bodies. You might not believe it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 213330.0,
      "end_time": 216330.0,
      "text": "but even our own bodies are radioactive enough to disturb this experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 216330.0,
      "end_time": 219330.0,
      "text": "So they go deep inside mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 219330.0,
      "end_time": 221330.0,
      "text": "to find a kind of environmental silence"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 221330.0,
      "end_time": 223330.0,
      "text": "that will allow them to hear"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 223330.0,
      "end_time": 226330.0,
      "text": "the ping of a dark matter particle hitting their detector."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 226330.0,
      "end_time": 228330.0,
      "text": "And I went to see one of these experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 228330.0,
      "end_time": 230330.0,
      "text": "and this is actually -- you can barely see it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 230330.0,
      "end_time": 233330.0,
      "text": "and the reason for that is it&#39;s entirely dark in there --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 233330.0,
      "end_time": 236330.0,
      "text": "this is a cavern that was left behind by the miners"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 236330.0,
      "end_time": 238330.0,
      "text": "who left this mine in 1960."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 238330.0,
      "end_time": 240330.0,
      "text": "And physicists came and started using it"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 240330.0,
      "end_time": 242330.0,
      "text": "sometime in the 1980s."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 242330.0,
      "end_time": 245330.0,
      "text": "And the miners in the early part of the last century"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 245330.0,
      "end_time": 247330.0,
      "text": "worked, literally, in candlelight."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 247330.0,
      "end_time": 249330.0,
      "text": "And today, you would see this inside the mine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 249330.0,
      "end_time": 251330.0,
      "text": "half a mile underground."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 251330.0,
      "end_time": 253330.0,
      "text": "This is one of the largest underground labs in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 253330.0,
      "end_time": 256330.0,
      "text": "And, among other things, they&#39;re looking for dark matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 256329.0,
      "end_time": 258329.0,
      "text": "There is another way to search for dark matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 258329.0,
      "end_time": 260329.0,
      "text": "which is indirectly."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 260329.0,
      "end_time": 262330.0,
      "text": "If dark matter exists in our universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 262330.0,
      "end_time": 264330.0,
      "text": "in our galaxy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 264330.0,
      "end_time": 266330.0,
      "text": "then these particles should be smashing together"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 266330.0,
      "end_time": 269330.0,
      "text": "and producing other particles that we know about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 269330.0,
      "end_time": 271330.0,
      "text": "one of them being neutrinos."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 271330.0,
      "end_time": 273330.0,
      "text": "And neutrinos you can detect"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 273330.0,
      "end_time": 275330.0,
      "text": "by the signature they leave"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 275330.0,
      "end_time": 277330.0,
      "text": "when they hit water molecules."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 277330.0,
      "end_time": 279330.0,
      "text": "When a neutrino hits a water molecule"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 279330.0,
      "end_time": 281330.0,
      "text": "it emits a kind of blue light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 281330.0,
      "end_time": 283330.0,
      "text": "a flash of blue light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 283330.0,
      "end_time": 285330.0,
      "text": "and by looking for this blue light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 285330.0,
      "end_time": 287330.0,
      "text": "you can essentially understand something about the neutrino"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 287330.0,
      "end_time": 290330.0,
      "text": "and then, indirectly, something about the dark matter"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 290330.0,
      "end_time": 292330.0,
      "text": "that might have created this neutrino."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 292330.0,
      "end_time": 295330.0,
      "text": "But you need very, very large volumes of water"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 295330.0,
      "end_time": 297330.0,
      "text": "in order to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 297330.0,
      "end_time": 299330.0,
      "text": "You need something like tens of megatons of water --"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 299330.0,
      "end_time": 301330.0,
      "text": "almost a gigaton of water --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 301330.0,
      "end_time": 304330.0,
      "text": "in order to have any chance of catching this neutrino."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 304330.0,
      "end_time": 306330.0,
      "text": "And where in the world would you find such water?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 306330.0,
      "end_time": 309330.0,
      "text": "Well the Russians have a tank in their own backyard."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 309330.0,
      "end_time": 311330.0,
      "text": "This is Lake Baikal."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 311330.0,
      "end_time": 314330.0,
      "text": "It is the largest lake in the world. It&#39;s 800 km long."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 314330.0,
      "end_time": 316330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about 40 to 50 km wide"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 316330.0,
      "end_time": 318330.0,
      "text": "in most places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 318330.0,
      "end_time": 320330.0,
      "text": "and one to two kilometers deep."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 320330.0,
      "end_time": 322330.0,
      "text": "And what the Russians are doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 322330.0,
      "end_time": 324330.0,
      "text": "is they&#39;re building these detectors"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 324330.0,
      "end_time": 327330.0,
      "text": "and immersing them about a kilometer beneath the surface of the lake"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 327330.0,
      "end_time": 330330.0,
      "text": "so that they can watch for these flashes of blue light."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 330330.0,
      "end_time": 333330.0,
      "text": "And this is the scene that greeted me when I landed there."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 333330.0,
      "end_time": 335330.0,
      "text": "This is Lake Baikal"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 335330.0,
      "end_time": 337330.0,
      "text": "in the peak of the Siberian winter."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 337330.0,
      "end_time": 339330.0,
      "text": "The lake is entirely frozen."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 339330.0,
      "end_time": 342330.0,
      "text": "And the line of black dots"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 342330.0,
      "end_time": 344330.0,
      "text": "that you see in the background,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 344330.0,
      "end_time": 346330.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the ice camp where the physicists are working."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 346330.0,
      "end_time": 348330.0,
      "text": "The reason why they have to work in winter"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 348330.0,
      "end_time": 351330.0,
      "text": "is because they don&#39;t have the money to work in summer and spring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 351330.0,
      "end_time": 353330.0,
      "text": "which, if they did that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 353330.0,
      "end_time": 355330.0,
      "text": "they would need ships and submersibles to do their work."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 355330.0,
      "end_time": 357330.0,
      "text": "So they wait until winter --"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 357330.0,
      "end_time": 359330.0,
      "text": "the lake is completely frozen over --"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 359330.0,
      "end_time": 361330.0,
      "text": "and they use this meter-thick ice"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 361330.0,
      "end_time": 364330.0,
      "text": "as a platform on which to establish their ice camp and do their work."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 364330.0,
      "end_time": 368330.0,
      "text": "So this is the Russians working on the ice"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 368330.0,
      "end_time": 370330.0,
      "text": "in the peak of the Siberian winter."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 370330.0,
      "end_time": 372330.0,
      "text": "They have to drill holes in the ice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 372330.0,
      "end_time": 374330.0,
      "text": "dive down into the water -- cold, cold water --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 374330.0,
      "end_time": 377330.0,
      "text": "to get hold of the instrument, bring it up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 377330.0,
      "end_time": 380330.0,
      "text": "do any repairs and maintenance that they need to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 380330.0,
      "end_time": 382330.0,
      "text": "put it back and get out before the ice melts."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 382330.0,
      "end_time": 384330.0,
      "text": "Because that phase of solid ice lasts for two months"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 384330.0,
      "end_time": 386330.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s full of cracks."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 386330.0,
      "end_time": 389330.0,
      "text": "And you have to imagine, there&#39;s an entire sea-like lake"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 389330.0,
      "end_time": 391330.0,
      "text": "underneath, moving."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 391330.0,
      "end_time": 394330.0,
      "text": "I still don&#39;t understand this one Russian man"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 394330.0,
      "end_time": 396330.0,
      "text": "working in his bare chest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 396330.0,
      "end_time": 399330.0,
      "text": "but that tells you how hard he was working."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 399330.0,
      "end_time": 401330.0,
      "text": "And these people, a handful of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 401330.0,
      "end_time": 403330.0,
      "text": "have been working for 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 403330.0,
      "end_time": 405330.0,
      "text": "looking for particles that may or may not exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 405330.0,
      "end_time": 408330.0,
      "text": "And they have dedicated their lives to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 408330.0,
      "end_time": 410330.0,
      "text": "And just to give you an idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 410330.0,
      "end_time": 413330.0,
      "text": "they have spent 20 million over 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 413330.0,
      "end_time": 415330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very harsh conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 415330.0,
      "end_time": 417330.0,
      "text": "They work on a shoestring budget."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 417330.0,
      "end_time": 419330.0,
      "text": "The toilets there are literally holes in the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 419330.0,
      "end_time": 422330.0,
      "text": "covered with a wooden shack."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 422330.0,
      "end_time": 424330.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s that basic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 424330.0,
      "end_time": 426330.0,
      "text": "but they do this every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 426330.0,
      "end_time": 429330.0,
      "text": "From Siberia to the Atacama Desert in Chile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 429330.0,
      "end_time": 431330.0,
      "text": "to see something called The Very Large Telescope."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 431330.0,
      "end_time": 433330.0,
      "text": "The Very Large Telescope"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 433330.0,
      "end_time": 435330.0,
      "text": "is one of these things that astronomers do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 435330.0,
      "end_time": 437330.0,
      "text": "they name their telescopes rather unimaginatively."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 437330.0,
      "end_time": 439330.0,
      "text": "I can tell you for a fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 439330.0,
      "end_time": 442330.0,
      "text": "that the next one that they&#39;re planning is called The Extremely Large Telescope."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 442330.0,
      "end_time": 444330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 444330.0,
      "end_time": 446330.0,
      "text": "And you wouldn&#39;t believe it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 446330.0,
      "end_time": 449330.0,
      "text": "but the one after that is going to be called The Overwhelmingly Large Telescope."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 449330.0,
      "end_time": 451330.0,
      "text": "But nonetheless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 451330.0,
      "end_time": 453330.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s an extraordinary piece of engineering."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 453330.0,
      "end_time": 456330.0,
      "text": "These are four 8.2 meter telescopes."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 456330.0,
      "end_time": 458330.0,
      "text": "And these telescopes, among other things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 458330.0,
      "end_time": 460330.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re being used to study"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 460330.0,
      "end_time": 463330.0,
      "text": "how the expansion of the universe is changing with time."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 463330.0,
      "end_time": 465330.0,
      "text": "And the more you understand that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 465330.0,
      "end_time": 467330.0,
      "text": "the better you would understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 467330.0,
      "end_time": 470330.0,
      "text": "what this dark energy that the universe is made of is all about."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 470330.0,
      "end_time": 473330.0,
      "text": "And one piece of engineering that I want to leave you with"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 473330.0,
      "end_time": 475330.0,
      "text": "as regards this telescope"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 475330.0,
      "end_time": 477330.0,
      "text": "is the mirror."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 477330.0,
      "end_time": 479330.0,
      "text": "Each mirror, there are four of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 479330.0,
      "end_time": 481330.0,
      "text": "is made of a single piece of glass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 481330.0,
      "end_time": 483330.0,
      "text": "a monolithic piece of high-tech ceramic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 483330.0,
      "end_time": 486330.0,
      "text": "that has been ground down and polished to such accuracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 486330.0,
      "end_time": 489330.0,
      "text": "that the only way to understand what that is"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 489330.0,
      "end_time": 491330.0,
      "text": "is [to] imagine a city like Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 491330.0,
      "end_time": 494330.0,
      "text": "with all its buildings and the Eiffel Tower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 494330.0,
      "end_time": 497330.0,
      "text": "if you grind down Paris to that kind of accuracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 497330.0,
      "end_time": 501330.0,
      "text": "you would be left with bumps that are one millimeter high."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 501330.0,
      "end_time": 504330.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the kind of polishing that these mirrors have endured."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 504330.0,
      "end_time": 506330.0,
      "text": "An extraordinary set of telescopes."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 506330.0,
      "end_time": 508330.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s another view of the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 508330.0,
      "end_time": 510330.0,
      "text": "The reason why you have to build these telescopes"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 510330.0,
      "end_time": 512329.0,
      "text": "in places like the Atacama Desert"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 512330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515330.00000000006,
      "text": "is because of the high altitude desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 515330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518330.00000000006,
      "text": "The dry air is really good for telescopes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 518330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520330.00000000006,
      "text": "and also, the cloud cover is below the summit of these mountains"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 520330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522330.00000000006,
      "text": "so that the telescopes have"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 522330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524330.0,
      "text": "about 300 days of clear skies."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 524330.0,
      "end_time": 526330.0,
      "text": "Finally, I want to take you to Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 526330.0,
      "end_time": 530330.0,
      "text": "I want to spend most of my time on this part of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 530330.0,
      "end_time": 532330.0,
      "text": "This is cosmology&#39;s final frontier."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 532330.0,
      "end_time": 534330.0,
      "text": "Some of the most amazing experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 534330.0,
      "end_time": 536330.0,
      "text": "some of the most extreme experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 536330.0,
      "end_time": 538330.0,
      "text": "are being done in Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 538330.0,
      "end_time": 541330.0,
      "text": "I was there to view something called a long-duration balloon flight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 541330.0,
      "end_time": 544330.0,
      "text": "which basically takes telescopes and instruments"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 544330.0,
      "end_time": 546330.0,
      "text": "all the way to the upper atmosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 546330.0,
      "end_time": 549330.0,
      "text": "the upper stratosphere, 40 km up."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 549330.0,
      "end_time": 551330.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s where they do their experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 551330.0,
      "end_time": 554330.0,
      "text": "and then the balloon, the payload, is brought down."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 554330.0,
      "end_time": 557330.0,
      "text": "So this is us landing on the Ross Ice Shelf in Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 557330.0,
      "end_time": 559330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an American C-17 cargo plane"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 559330.0,
      "end_time": 561330.0,
      "text": "that flew us from New Zealand"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 561330.0,
      "end_time": 563330.0,
      "text": "to McMurdo in Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 563330.0,
      "end_time": 565330.0,
      "text": "And here we are about to board our bus."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 565330.0,
      "end_time": 567330.0,
      "text": "And I don&#39;t know if you can read the lettering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 567330.0,
      "end_time": 570330.0,
      "text": "but it says, \"Ivan the Terribus.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 570330.0,
      "end_time": 573330.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s taking us to McMurdo."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 573330.0,
      "end_time": 576330.0,
      "text": "And this is the scene that greets you in McMurdo."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 576330.0,
      "end_time": 578330.0,
      "text": "And you barely might be able to make out"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 578330.0,
      "end_time": 580330.0,
      "text": "this hut here."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 580330.0,
      "end_time": 583330.0,
      "text": "This hut was built by Robert Falcon Scott and his men"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 583330.0,
      "end_time": 585330.0,
      "text": "when they first came to Antarctica"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 585330.0,
      "end_time": 587330.0,
      "text": "on their first expedition to go to the South Pole."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 587330.0,
      "end_time": 589330.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s so cold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 589330.0,
      "end_time": 592330.0,
      "text": "the entire contents of that hut is still as they left it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 592330.0,
      "end_time": 595330.0,
      "text": "with the remnants of the last meal they cooked still there."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 595330.0,
      "end_time": 597330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an extraordinary place."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 597330.0,
      "end_time": 600330.0,
      "text": "This is McMurdo itself. About a thousand people work here in summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 600330.0,
      "end_time": 602330.0,
      "text": "and about 200 in winter"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 602330.0,
      "end_time": 604330.0,
      "text": "when it&#39;s completely dark for six months."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 604330.0,
      "end_time": 606330.0,
      "text": "I was here to see the launch"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 606330.0,
      "end_time": 608330.0,
      "text": "of this particular type of instrument."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 608330.0,
      "end_time": 610330.0,
      "text": "This is a cosmic ray experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 610330.0,
      "end_time": 613330.0,
      "text": "that has been launched all the way to the upper-stratosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 613330.0,
      "end_time": 615330.0,
      "text": "to an altitude of 40 km."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 615330.0,
      "end_time": 618330.0,
      "text": "What I want you to imagine is this is two tons in weight."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 618330.0,
      "end_time": 620330.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;re using a balloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 620330.0,
      "end_time": 622330.0,
      "text": "to carry something that is two tons"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 622330.0,
      "end_time": 625330.0,
      "text": "all the way to an altitude of 40 km."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 625330.0,
      "end_time": 628330.0,
      "text": "And the engineers, the technicians, the physicists"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 628330.0,
      "end_time": 631330.0,
      "text": "have all got to assemble on the Ross Ice Shelf,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 631330.0,
      "end_time": 634330.0,
      "text": "because Antarctica -- I won&#39;t go into the reasons why --"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 634330.0,
      "end_time": 636330.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s one of the most favorable places for doing these balloon launches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 636330.0,
      "end_time": 638330.0,
      "text": "except for the weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 638330.0,
      "end_time": 640330.0,
      "text": "The weather, as you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 640330.0,
      "end_time": 642330.0,
      "text": "this is summer, and you&#39;re standing on 200 ft of ice."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 642330.0,
      "end_time": 644330.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s a volcano behind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 644330.0,
      "end_time": 646330.0,
      "text": "which has glaciers at the very top."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 646330.0,
      "end_time": 648330.0,
      "text": "And what they have to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 648330.0,
      "end_time": 650330.0,
      "text": "is they have to assemble the entire balloon --"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 650330.0,
      "end_time": 653330.0,
      "text": "the fabric, parachute and everything -- on the ice"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 653330.0,
      "end_time": 655330.0,
      "text": "and then fill it up with helium."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 655330.0,
      "end_time": 657330.0,
      "text": "And that process takes about two hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 657330.0,
      "end_time": 660330.0,
      "text": "And the weather can change as they&#39;re putting together this whole assembly."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 660330.0,
      "end_time": 663330.0,
      "text": "For instance, here they are laying down the balloon fabric behind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 663330.0,
      "end_time": 666330.0,
      "text": "which is eventually going to be filled up with helium."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 666330.0,
      "end_time": 668330.0,
      "text": "Those two trucks you see at the very end"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 668330.0,
      "end_time": 671330.0,
      "text": "carry 12 tanks each of compressed helium."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 671330.0,
      "end_time": 674330.0,
      "text": "Now, in case the weather changes before the launch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 674330.0,
      "end_time": 677330.0,
      "text": "they have to actually pack everything back up into their boxes"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 677330.0,
      "end_time": 680330.0,
      "text": "and take it out back to McMurdo Station."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 680330.0,
      "end_time": 682330.0,
      "text": "And this particular balloon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 682330.0,
      "end_time": 684330.0,
      "text": "because it has to launch two tons of weight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 684330.0,
      "end_time": 687330.0,
      "text": "is an extremely huge balloon."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 687330.0,
      "end_time": 689330.0,
      "text": "The fabric alone weighs two tons."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 689330.0,
      "end_time": 692330.0,
      "text": "In order to minimize the weight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 692330.0,
      "end_time": 694330.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s very thin, it&#39;s as thin as a sandwich wrapper."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 694330.0,
      "end_time": 696330.0,
      "text": "And if they have to pack it back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 696330.0,
      "end_time": 698330.0,
      "text": "they have to put it into boxes"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 698330.0,
      "end_time": 701330.0,
      "text": "and stamp on it so that it fits into the box again --"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 701330.0,
      "end_time": 703330.0,
      "text": "except, when they did it first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 703330.0,
      "end_time": 705330.0,
      "text": "it would have been done in Texas."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 705330.0,
      "end_time": 708330.0,
      "text": "Here, they can&#39;t do it with the kind shoes they&#39;re wearing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 708330.0,
      "end_time": 710330.0,
      "text": "so they have to take their shoes off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 710330.0,
      "end_time": 712330.0,
      "text": "get barefoot into the boxes, in this cold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 712330.0,
      "end_time": 714330.0,
      "text": "and do that kind of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 714330.0,
      "end_time": 716330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the kind of dedication these people have."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 716330.0,
      "end_time": 718330.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s the balloon being filled up with helium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 718330.0,
      "end_time": 720330.0,
      "text": "and you can see it&#39;s a gorgeous sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 720330.0,
      "end_time": 722330.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a scene"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 722330.0,
      "end_time": 724330.0,
      "text": "that shows you the balloon and the payload end-to-end."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 724330.0,
      "end_time": 727330.0,
      "text": "So the balloon is being filled up with helium on the left-hand side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 727330.0,
      "end_time": 730330.0,
      "text": "and the fabric actually runs all the way to the middle"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 730330.0,
      "end_time": 733330.0,
      "text": "where there&#39;s a piece of electronics and explosives"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 733330.0,
      "end_time": 735330.0,
      "text": "being connected to a parachute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 735330.0,
      "end_time": 737330.0,
      "text": "and then the parachute is then connected to the payload."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 737330.0,
      "end_time": 739330.0,
      "text": "And remember, all this wiring is being done"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 739330.0,
      "end_time": 742330.0,
      "text": "by people in extreme cold, in sub-zero temperatures."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 742330.0,
      "end_time": 745330.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re wearing about 15 kg of clothing and stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 745330.0,
      "end_time": 748330.0,
      "text": "but they have to take their gloves off in order to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 748330.0,
      "end_time": 751330.0,
      "text": "And I would like to share with you a launch."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 751330.0,
      "end_time": 753330.0,
      "text": "(Video) Radio: Okay, release the balloon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 753330.0,
      "end_time": 756330.0,
      "text": "release the balloon, release the balloon."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 784330.0,
      "end_time": 787330.0,
      "text": "Anil Ananthaswamy: And I&#39;ll finally like to leave you with two images."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 787330.0,
      "end_time": 790330.0,
      "text": "This is an observatory in the Himalayas, in Ladakh in India."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 790330.0,
      "end_time": 792330.0,
      "text": "And the thing I want you to look at here"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 792330.0,
      "end_time": 794330.0,
      "text": "is the telescope on the right-hand side."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 794330.0,
      "end_time": 796330.0,
      "text": "And on the far left there"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 796330.0,
      "end_time": 798330.0,
      "text": "is a 400 year-old Buddhist monastery."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 798330.0,
      "end_time": 800330.0,
      "text": "This is a close-up of the Buddhist monastery."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 800330.0,
      "end_time": 803330.0,
      "text": "And I was struck by the juxtaposition"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 803330.0,
      "end_time": 806330.0,
      "text": "of these two enormous disciplines that humanity has."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 806330.0,
      "end_time": 809330.0,
      "text": "One is exploring the cosmos on the outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 809330.0,
      "end_time": 811330.0,
      "text": "and the other one is exploring our interior being."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 811330.0,
      "end_time": 814330.0,
      "text": "And both require silence of some sort."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 814330.0,
      "end_time": 816330.0,
      "text": "And what struck me was"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 816330.0,
      "end_time": 818330.0,
      "text": "every place that I went to to see these telescopes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 818330.0,
      "end_time": 820330.0,
      "text": "the astronomers and cosmologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 820330.0,
      "end_time": 822330.0,
      "text": "are in search of a certain kind of silence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 822330.0,
      "end_time": 824330.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s silence from radio pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 824330.0,
      "end_time": 827330.0,
      "text": "or light pollution or whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 827330.0,
      "end_time": 829330.0,
      "text": "And it was very obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 829330.0,
      "end_time": 831330.0,
      "text": "that, if we destroy these silent places on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 332,
      "start_time": 831330.0,
      "end_time": 834330.0,
      "text": "we will be stuck on a planet without the ability to look outwards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 333,
      "start_time": 834330.0,
      "end_time": 837330.0,
      "text": "because we will not be able to understand the signals that come from outer space."
    },
    {
      "index": 334,
      "start_time": 837330.0,
      "end_time": 839330.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 335,
      "start_time": 839330.0,
      "end_time": 842330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}